     YAML Basics

YAML Is not a Markup language
YAML is used to store information about different things
We can use YAML to define key value pairs like variables , list and objects
YAML is very similar to JSON
YAML primilary focuses on readability and user friendliness

We can define yaml files with two different extensions
  1. abc.yml
  2. abc.yaml


The keys things of yaml are 

1. YAML Comments
2. YAML key value pairs
3. YAML Dictionary or map
4. YAML Array
5. YAML Spaces
6. YAML Document Seperator
